&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Protect and build a future shaped by original ideas, innovations, and creativity.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Threats to brand integrity are scaling fast. We&#39;re building the intelligence to scale faster. MarqVision is the brand integrity partner for the world&#39;s most ambitious companies, providing AI-powered enforcement and intelligence across 1,500+ platforms in 115+ countries. We don&#39;t just flag problems; we eliminate them at scale so brands can grow with confidence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2020 by Harvard Law graduates and backed by leading investors including SoftBank, Y Combinator, DST Global Partners, HSG, and Salesforce Ventures, we&#39;ve built the category-defining platform for brand protection. We&#39;re recognized with an LVMH Innovation Award and named to the Inc. 5000 Fastest Growing Companies in 2025, and we&#39;re just getting started.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to work at the intersection of AI, global commerce, and IP, this is the place. We&#39;re pushing the boundaries of brand control to keep innovation, creativity, and trust safeguarded in a rapidly evolving digital world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consult prospective clients on tailored brand protection strategies and how MarqVision&#39;s platform addresses their specific challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver compelling product demonstrations that bring to life the platform&#39;s ability to detect, enforce against, and eliminate counterfeit activity at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead high-quality discovery calls, business reviews, and demo sessions with potential customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own pipeline progression and closing new business against quarterly revenue targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Sales Development Representatives to execute strategic outbound campaigns&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Account Management team to identify and close expansion opportunities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of closing experience in a B2B SaaS sales role, with a consistent track record of meeting or exceeding quarterly revenue targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to manage complex, consultative sales cycles of 3–6 months and close deals with ACVs in the £37,000–£112,000 range&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confident and proactive pipeline building, comfort self-sourcing opportunities alongside SDR support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience engaging and influencing senior executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Signal&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in Spanish or German&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of closing enterprise-level accounts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sector experience in fashion, cosmetics, or other consumer products&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with intellectual property, brand protection, or anti-counterfeiting, whether through prior roles or genuine personal interest&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practical application of structured sales methodologies (i.e. MEDDPIC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Become a Marqvisioner&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous PTO to take the time you need, when you need it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hybrid work model designed for focus and flexibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Equity in every offer — because you should own a piece of what you&#39;re building&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive health, dental, and vision coverage, plus parental leave to support your life outside of work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pension plan to help you save for the future&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A one-time home office stipend for remote employees — because your setup should work as hard as you do&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Protect what&#39;s original. Scale what&#39;s possible. At MarqV

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;独自のアイデア、革新、そして創造性によって形作られる未来を守り、築いていく。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;模倣品や海賊版コンテンツ、不正サイト、非正規流通など、あらゆるリスクからブランドを守るため、MarqVisionはEコマース・SNS・新興AIプラットフォームにわたるエンドツーエンドのブランド保護プラットフ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ォームを提供しています。AIを活用したマネージドサービス型のブランドコントロール・インテリジェンスプラットフォームにより、ブランドはすべてのデジタルタッチポイントにおいて、迅速かつスケーラブルなエンフォースメントを実現し、収益の保護とブランドエクイティの維持が可能になります。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;知財侵害がますます深刻な課題となる現代において、法的専門知識と最新の生成AI技術へのアクセスを一般レベルで運用化することが、安全で高品質なプロダクトを届けるために日々努力する世界中の発明家・開発者・アーティストを支え続けるために不可欠だと私たちは考えています。2020年にハーバード・ロースクール卒業生によって創業されたMarqVisionは、シリーズBの資金調達を完了し、累計調達額は$89M（約140億円）に達しました。Y Combinator、Peak XV（旧Sequoia Capital India）、HSG（旧Sequoia Capital China）、Salesforce Ventures、Altos Ventures、DST Global Partners、SoftBankが出資しています。2025年にはLVMHイノベーション賞およびInc 5000最速成長企業に選出され、急速に進化するデジタル世界において革新・創造性・信頼が守られ続けるよう、ブランドコントロールの限界に挑み続けています。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;日本では、主要なエンタープライズ企業に導入が進み、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/posts/insup_brandprotection-ai-aiservices-share-7463265651818803200-cbdL/?utm_source=share&amp;amp;utm_medium=member_desktop&amp;amp;rcm=ACoAABqIRj4BRCrtTFGHo03XraK5tZLeVPRmIy4&quot;&gt;（Panasonic&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/posts/insup_brandprotection-ai-counterfeit-share-7465421497709301761-mRXH/?utm_source=share&amp;amp;utm_medium=member_desktop&amp;amp;rcm=ACoAABqIRj4BRCrtTFGHo03XraK5tZLeVPRmIy4&quot;&gt;日産自動車&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/posts/insup_brandprotection-ai-aiservices-share-7462524099098054656-1LmN/?utm_source=share&amp;amp;utm_medium=member_desktop&amp;amp;rcm=ACoAABqIRj4BRCrtTFGHo03XraK5tZLeVPRmIy4&quot;&gt;セガ&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/posts/marqvision-is-thrilled-to-announce-that-weve-share-7441788233643970560--WO-/?utm_source=share&amp;amp;utm_medium=member_desktop&amp;amp;rcm=ACoAABqIRj4BRCrtTFGHo03XraK5tZLeVPRmIy4&quot;&gt;ミズノ&lt;/a&gt;,他多数）などの日本を代表するトップブランドを顧客に連ね、自動車、ファッション、ゲーム、化粧品、産業機器など、多岐にわたる業界のリーディングカンパニーを支援しています。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2025年より本格的な日本展開を始め、カテゴリーリーダーとしての地位を確立し、共に市場を切り拓いていく創業期メンバーを募集しています。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;業務内容 / How You&#39;ll Make an Impact at MarqVision&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ファッション、エンタメから製造業まで、世界的なブランドが直面する模倣品や偽サイトの被害を包括的に解決する&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;最先端AIテクノロジーを駆使し、オンライン・オフラインを問わず不正な流通経路を徹底的に排除する&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;国内および欧米のセールスリーダーと緊密に連携を図り、戦略的なエンタープライズ案件を成約へ導く&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;知財、コマーシャル部門、経営層、海外拠点などの多岐にわたるステークホルダーを統括し、プロジェクトを主導する&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ソリューション提案から製品デモ、契約交渉、クローズに至るまでの新規顧客開拓を一貫して担う&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;実証実験（PoC）を通じて価値を証明し、年間契約へのスムーズな移行を完遂する&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;カスタマーサクセスやアナリストチームと協働し、既存顧客に対する更なる提供価値の拡大を推進する&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;※セールスサイクル：3〜6ヶ月、平均契約単価：$50k〜$200k（約750万〜3,000万円）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;応募資格 / Skills You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;B2B SaaS領域における5年以上のエンタープライズ向け新規営業・成約経験&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;四半期ごとのKPIおよび営業目標を継続的に達成してきた確かなトラックレコード&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CXO層や経営層に対する、ビジネス課題に基づいた高度な提案・交渉能力&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;IS部門との連携に加え、自律的にパイプラインを構築し商談化できるセールス経験&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;製造業や大手ブランドメーカーを対象とした営業経験があれば尚可&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;エンタープライズ市場で自走しながらパイプラインを創出できる方（インサイドセールス連携も可）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;グローバルチームと円滑に合意形成・協働が可能なビジネスレベルの英語力&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;歓迎する経験・スキル / Nice to Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;知的財産（IP）やブランドの保護領域に対する深い関心、あるいは実務経験&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ラグジュアリー、ファッション、エンターテインメント、自動車から重工業まで、多角的な産業分野でのセールスキャリア&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;世界を舞台に展開するグローバルブランドを対象とした、戦略的なフロント営業の経験&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BANTやROI等のセールスプロセスを高度に管理し、ステークホルダーが複雑に絡む大型案件を成約へ導く実行力&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;知的探究心があり、チームに活力を与えるポジティブかつユーモアのある方&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;なぜこのAEポジションか / Why MarqVision?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;「AIによるブランド保護」という新領域で、カテゴリーリーダーとして圧倒

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Protecting and building a future shaped by original ideas, innovations, and creativity.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From counterfeits and pirated content to fraudulent sites and unauthorized sellers, MarqVision provides an end-to-end brand integrity platform across e-commerce, social media and emerging AI platforms. Our AI-powered managed service platform for brand control and intelligence enables rapid, scalable enforcement so that brands can move faster, protect revenue, and preserve brand equity across every digital touchpoint. In a time when IP infringements pose an increasingly serious challenge, we believe that democratizing legal expertise and access to the latest in generative AI technology is critical for continuing to support the inventors, developers, and artists of the world who work tirelessly to deliver safe, high-quality products.&amp;nbsp;Founded by Harvard Law graduates in 2020, MarqVision recently raised Series B, bringing total funding to $89M, and is backed by Y Combinator, Peak XV (formerly Sequoia Capital India), HSG (formerly Sequoia Capital China), Salesforce Ventures, Altos Ventures, DST Global Partners, and Softbank. Recognized with an LVMH Innovation Award and the Inc 5000 Fastest Growing Companies award in 2025, MarqVision continues to push boundaries in brand control, ensuring that innovation, creativity, and trust remain safeguarded in a rapidly evolving digital world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You’ll Make an Impact at MarqVision&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MarqVision is looking for Brand Analysts to join our Shanghai office. In this role, you&#39;ll safeguard our client&#39;s intellectual property rights in the digital landscape. Working under the guidance of an Customer Success Manager or Team Lead, you&#39;ll leverage your investigative skills to actively search for and monitor online activities that infringe on client copyrights, trademarks, or patents. Utilizing your analytical abilities, you&#39;ll compare the gathered data against client-defined parameters to determine the most effective course of action.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Achieve&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Online IP Investigations: &lt;/strong&gt;You&#39;ll become a digital detective, actively searching for and monitoring potential online infringements of client copyrights, trademarks, or patents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Enforcement:&lt;/strong&gt; Analyzing data against client-defined parameters, you&#39;ll recommend the most effective course of action.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Direct Takedowns:&lt;/strong&gt; For clear-cut cases, you&#39;ll initiate swift takedown requests to remove infringing content from online platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Targeted Investigations:&lt;/strong&gt; When evidence requires further digging, you&#39;ll conduct additional research to solidify the case.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Takedown Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;ll collaborate with major e-commerce sites, filing complaints and requesting the removal of infringing goods. You&#39;ll also prepare all necessary documentation to support these takedown requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Knowledge Sharing:&lt;/strong&gt; For the benefit of the team, you&#39;ll develop templates and best practices for efficient IP protection strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adaptability &amp;amp; Initiative:&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;ll be prepared to tackle additional tasks assigned by your Line Manager, demonstrating your adaptability and willingness to take initiative.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills You Bring&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive and self-driven working style.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in IP-related career.&lt;/li&g

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Protecting and building a future shaped by original ideas, innovations, and creativity.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From counterfeits and pirated content to fraudulent sites and unauthorized sellers, MarqVision provides end-to-end brand control across 1,500+ platforms in 118+ countries. Our AI-powered managed service platform for brand control and intelligence enables rapid, scalable enforcement—so your team can move faster, protect revenue, and preserve brand equity across every digital touchpoint. Founded by Harvard Law graduates in 2020, MarqVision is backed by Peak XV (formerly Sequoia Capital India), HSG (formerly Sequoia Capital China), Salesforce Ventures, Altos Ventures, DST Global Partners, Y Combinator, Softbank and Atinum Investments. Recognized with an LVMH Innovation Award and the Inc 5000 Fastest Growing Companies award in 2025, MarqVision continues to push boundaries in brand control, ensuring that innovation, creativity, and trust remain safeguarded in a rapidly evolving digital world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How&amp;nbsp;You&#39;ll&amp;nbsp;Make&amp;nbsp;an&amp;nbsp;Impact&amp;nbsp;at&amp;nbsp;MarqVision&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Marq AI is looking for a Brand Protection Investigator to join our Legal and Expert Services Team. In this role, you will report to the Expert Services Team Lead and be responsible for conducting investigations for brand protection as well as coordinating with partner firms around the world to conduct test purchases and send demand letters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Achieve&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct investigative Test Purchases and write reports for clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate with global partners regarding legal actions for clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate internally to facilitate on-going investigations for clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct research on sellers online, as well as different IP laws around the world.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate actions against counterfeit sellers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage database of ongoing cases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide/assist in providing any other brand protection services as required by our customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills You&#39;ll Need to Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to fluently read, write, and speak English and Chinese in a business environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work well under pressure and tight deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to conduct work according to provided guidelines accurately and with minimum mistakes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a multicultural environment, handling work in different time zones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reside in China to be able to conduct and receive test purchase products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a legal environment such as Law Firms or Corporate Legal Teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience with authentication of counterfeit goods or any related investigative work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to read and write Korean.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Reference&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.marqvision.com/blog&quot;&gt;MarqVision Company Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.marqvision.com/leadership&quot;&gt;Leadership Team&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Equal Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At MarqVision, we believe real growth comes with attracting the brightest minds, motivating them to succeed

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Protecting and building a future shaped by original ideas, innovations, and creativity.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From counterfeits and pirated content to fraudulent sites and unauthorized sellers, MarqVision provides an end-to-end brand integrity platform across e-commerce, social media and emerging AI platforms. Our AI-powered managed service platform for brand control and intelligence enables rapid, scalable enforcement so that brands can move faster, protect revenue, and preserve brand equity across every digital touchpoint. In a time when IP infringements pose an increasingly serious challenge, we believe that democratizing legal expertise and access to the latest in generative AI technology is critical for continuing to support the inventors, developers, and artists of the world who work tirelessly to deliver safe, high-quality products.&amp;nbsp;Founded by Harvard Law graduates in 2020, MarqVision recently raised Series B, bringing total funding to $89M, and is backed by Y Combinator, Peak XV (formerly Sequoia Capital India), HSG (formerly Sequoia Capital China), Salesforce Ventures, Altos Ventures, DST Global Partners, and Softbank. Recognized with an LVMH Innovation Award and the Inc 5000 Fastest Growing Companies award in 2025, MarqVision continues to push boundaries in brand control, ensuring that innovation, creativity, and trust remain safeguarded in a rapidly evolving digital world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You’ll Make an Impact at MarqVision&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brand Protection Specialist는 글로벌 브랜드를 위협하는 다양한 디지털 리스크로부터 브랜드의 지식재산권을 보호하는 핵심적인 역할을 합니다. AI 기반 기술을 활용하여 위조품, 사칭, 불법 복제, 무단 판매 등의 침해 행위를 감지하고 대응하며, 고객사에 최적화된 보호 전략을 제공합니다. 또한, 주요 사용자로서 솔루션의 지속적인 개선을 위한 피드백을 제공하고, 브랜드 보호 기술의 발전에 기여할 수 있습니다. 빠르게 변화하는 글로벌 스타트업 환경 속에서 도전적인 과제들을 해결하며 브랜드 보호의 미래를 함께 만들어 나갈 기회를 얻게 될 것입니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Achieve&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;온라인 마켓플레이스, 소셜 미디어 및 기타 디지털 플랫폼에서 위조품, 사칭, 불법 복제, 무단 판매를 모니터링하고 브랜드 보호 행위를 시행합니다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI 기반 브랜드 보호 솔루션의 발전과 효율성 향상을 위해 주요 사용자로서 피드백을 제공하고, 솔루션 개선에 기여합니다.&lt;/li&gt;
