&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Marqvision&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Protect and build a future shaped by original ideas, innovations and creativity.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Threats to brand integrity are scaling fast. We&#39;re building the intelligence to scale faster. MarqVision is the brand integrity partner for the world&#39;s most ambitious companies, providing AI-powered enforcement and intelligence across 1,500+ platforms in 115+ countries. We don&#39;t just flag problems; we eliminate them at scale so brands can grow with confidence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2020 by Harvard Law graduates and backed by leading investors including SoftBank, Y Combinator, DST Global Partners, HSG, and Salesforce Ventures, we&#39;ve built the category-defining platform for brand protection. We&#39;re recognized with an LVMH Innovation Award and named to the Inc. 5000 Fastest Growing Companies in 2025, and we&#39;re just getting started.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to work at the intersection of AI, global commerce, and IP, this is the place. We&#39;re pushing the boundaries of brand control to keep innovation, creativity, and trust safeguarded in a rapidly evolving digital world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You&#39;ll Make an Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a Content Lead to drive the next phase of MarqVision&#39;s storytelling and audience growth. This goes beyond publishing: your mission is to build lifecycle ecosystems around our most important insights, research, and customer stories, turning content into an engine for awareness, engagement, and pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll own our always-on content strategy across video, social, email, and influencer partnerships, getting our best ideas to the right audiences repeatedly, in formats they actually consume. A major plus: using AI-powered workflows to systematize creation, repurposing, and distribution, so one insight becomes multi-channel storytelling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is public-facing too, so if you like the spotlight, you&#39;ll get your moment: hosting webinars, moderating customer discussions, interviewing industry experts, and appearing in video and social content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain MarqVision’s brand voice and editorial guidelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a content ecosystem around flagship assets (research, case studies, webinars, and events) created with support from product marketing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure consistent storytelling across video, social, email, and owned channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Together with our Growth team, strategize on an always-on program across short-form video, LinkedIn and social storytelling, email insights, newsletters, industry commentary and trend analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage a network of industry influencers and creators across E-commerce, marketplaces, brand protection, cybersecurity, gaming and digital IP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years in content marketing, media, journalism, or storytelling roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of B2B marketing and audience development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional storytelling and editorial instincts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with video, social media, and creator-led content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort appearing on camera or hosting conversations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to translate complex topics like IP law into clear, engaging narratives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic thinking and executing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
