&lt;li&gt;Build the bench from the ground up — recruiting, hiring, and developing a team of San Francisco-based Enterprise Account Executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead from the front on marquee deals, multi-threading across legal/IP, brand protection, Trust &amp;amp; Safety, marketing, and procurement to win at the enterprise level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install a disciplined sales methodology (MEDDPICC, Command of the Message) and hold the team to clean pipeline, forecasting, and Salesforce hygiene&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Protect and grow average enterprise ACV by structuring deals that reflect the full value of the platform — winning on value, not price&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver an accurate, trustworthy forecast and roll-up to the Global Head of Sales and CEO&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Product, Customer Success, and RevOps to align the go-to-market motion and clear the path to clos&lt;/li&gt;
